    "body": "Maximum length doesn't make too much sense IMO.\r\nLinks can be long. Although I do see we don't expect very long links in this case.\r\n\r\nThere's a few ways to go about this, but if we know for sure that some of these links are twitter, linkedin, github etc, then check if the fields contain valid github/twitter user URLs.\r\n\r\nEven better, don't ask the user to put a full twitter/github URL there if we know it's an input for twitter/github, just let them enter the username and have the app store the full URL if necessary",
